*Promena* se desila preko noći. (The change happened overnight.)
Ljudska *promena* je neophodna. (Human change is necessary.)
Ovo je prilika za *promenu*. (This is an opportunity for change.)
Postoji *promena* u njegovom ponašanju. (There is a change in his behavior.)
Moramo da se prilagodimo *promeni*. (We must adapt to the change.)